---
title: Old Fashioned Ham Steak with Pineapple and Sweet Potatoes
description: Sticky, sweet and salty ham gets a truly retro glaze of mustard, brown sugar and brûléed pineapple. Quick sweet potato mash and buttery roasted green beans will have you feeling nostalgic.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/old-fashioned-ham-steak-ca36e074.jpg
